SUB_W15_EVAR_BOFO_TERMINAL_000_CUT_000_1.text:
We should finish the repairs quickly;
the explosion's impact is already
spreading across the land.

SUB_W15_EVAR_BOFO_LAB_GOTERMINAL_000_CUT.text:
Let's hold off telling Corana about this;
I don't want to introduce a bunch of chaos
and doubt into her life if we don't have to.

SUB_W15_EVAR_BOFO_PORT_000_CUT_000_010.text:
If you're offering, I'm glad for the help;
the engine is one of the older models,
and restarting it is a lot of work.

SUB_W15_EVAR_BOFO_TRADE_END_000_CUT_000_.text:
The system has restarted without issue;
perhaps because we defeated such a
large number of fiends.

SUB_W15_EVAR_BOFO_ALESSAAGHOST_000_CUT_0.text:
I don't want Fred to know we heard him talking;
he might change his plans if he found out,
and we need to know what those plans are.
